    'Data schema guide:\n- `window`: `{start_ts, end_ts, timezone, rows_analyzed}` for analysis scope.\n- `summary`: compact metrics for quick interpretation.\n- `narrative_hints`: deterministic cues from analytics logic; treat as guidance, not hard facts.\n- Outlier context includes `baseline_stats`, `outlier_events`, and `cost_anomalies`.',
